title: Live in a Community w/Tons of Perks! Awesome 2Bedroom Apt Home!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Park Haven Apartments!', 'A pet-friendly apartment community located in Brooklyn Park, MN.', 'Park Haven offers our residents a variety of apartment and community amenities to explore.', 'From our gorgeous community clubhouse to our on-site fitness center there is something for everyone to enjoy!', 'We offer spacious 1, 2 and 3 bedroom floor plan options to choose from.', 'Each floor plan showcases luxury vinyl wood plank flooring, beautiful kitchen cabinetry & countertops, and large bedrooms with ample closet space in each home.', 'We keep comfort and quality in mind at the Oaks Landing.', 'Call our management office to learn more today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Beautiful Kitchen Cabinetry & Updated Countertops (select homes)', '- Heat, Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Services', 'Included', '- Two Outdoor Playground Areas', '- Designer Lighting & Hardware Package', '- Fitness Center', '- Central Heating & Air-Conditioning System', '- Controlled Access Entry System', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Park Haven Apartments participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $76,020.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Tuesday: 9:00AM-1:00PM', 'Wednesday-Thursday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Friday: 9:00AM-1:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Park Haven Apartments', '6917 76th Avenue North', 'Brooklyn Park, MN, 55428', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'ol8ctrZF6PZ']
